# NOTE: src/shared/ holds generated copies of the repo-root engine + datasets.
# They are COMMITTED (not ignored) so EAS cloud builds always have them.
# Source of truth remains the repo-root files; re-run `npm run sync-shared`
# (auto-runs before start/build) after editing flight-engine.js or shots.json.

